                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(center)\">\n                                        <addressee>Mr. Leeser</addressee>\n                                        <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>Norfolk</placeName>\n                                        <date>Mai 14 50</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>According my <sic>promisse</sic> to try my best<lb/> for you I give\n                                        you a <sic>smal</sic> order.<lb/> Few Jews in\n                                                  <sic>habitence</sic>\n                                        <sic>spocke</sic> to me for<lb/> some <add>תפלות</add>\n                                        <sic>german</sic>\n                                        <add>מנהג</add> with <sic>english</sic> translation.<lb/>\n                                        but they don't want to spend more as two<lb/> dollar a\n                                        piece. If you can comply with said<lb/> price you may send\n                                        3. if not I could<lb/> sell 1 at $2.50 &amp; also I could\n                                        sell<lb/> for you <add>חמשה חומשי תורה</add> translated in\n                                                  <sic>english</sic><lb/> for 5-6 dollars. I don't\n                                        want to make<lb/> anything by it, just only as a favour\n                                        to<lb/> you. If you send something, please let me know<lb/>\n                                        how to send the money for it.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(6)\">It remains your obt frid</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(7)\"><persName role=\"author\">M\n                                        Dannonberg</persName>.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"Next line added in pencil\">tefelot minhag <add>?</add></p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3s757550/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
